---
title: Easy Chicken Tray-Bake with Roast Veggies, Salad and Mango Chutney Yoghurt
description: The trick to this tray bake is to make sure everything is well spread out. Giving the chicken and veggies enough room is important as it ensures they get lovely crispy edges. Use two trays if you need to, swapping round their position in the oven halfway through cooking.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-chicken-tray-bake-78985b51.jpg
